Imagawayaki

46
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:12,200
He's been eating out a lot since elementary school.

47
00:03:13,270 --> 00:03:16,550
The soy-flour candy at that
 candy store in front of the school...

48
00:03:16,550 --> 00:03:19,000
That was the best ever.

49
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,240
Wow.

50
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:24,560
Hiro would put so many of them into his mouth at once that he'd choke on them.

51
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:28,950
He kept wheezing, so the candy store lady called an ambulance one time.

52
00:03:29,940 --> 00:03:31,750
That happened ?

53
00:03:32,410 --> 00:03:33,760
Shut up.

54
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:40,080
Hey, is your elementary
 school far from here ?

55
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:42,010
No, it's just a ten-minute walk.

56
00:03:42,010 --> 00:03:43,580
I want to see it.

57
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:45,340
I don't want to see it.

58
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:52,720
Oh, I should show you the 
graduation totem pole that Hiro broke.

59
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,700
What's that ?

60
00:03:54,350 --> 00:03:58,250
