Snow...

64
00:04:17,610 --> 00:04:18,740
What was that ?

65
00:04:20,470 --> 00:04:21,600
Hey, Hiro !

66
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,980
You're not coming, Kunimi ?

67
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:28,200
I guess I'll go.

