We used to make throws
 from here to those iron bars.

81
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:57,160
When you were in elementary school ?

82
00:05:57,160 --> 00:06:00,200
We reached there when we 
were in fifth grade, right, Noda ?

83
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:04,500
Even when you were
 little, you were amazing.

84
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:05,550
Shall we make a throw ?

85
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,520
All right.

86
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:17,500
Here I go !

87
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:19,810
Okay !

88
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,750
Hiro, here it comes !

89
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:03,000
Like that elm tree, I...

90
