Hiro !

95
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:20,290
What was it ?

96
00:07:21,970 --> 00:07:22,870
Kunimi ?

97
00:07:31,230 --> 00:07:32,270
I forgot.

98
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:48,270
Please.

99
00:07:52,990 --> 00:07:54,700
You're back, clean-up guy.

100
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,400
Yes.

101
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,450
Please.

102
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,310
All right.

103
00:08:15,970 --> 00:08:17,470
Rehab is complete.

104
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:23,230
Amamiya Hikari,
 thanks for your work.

