00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:16,310
Ugh...!

270
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:21,260
All the powerhouse schools 
have indoor workout facilities.

271
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:25,610
If this weather continues, 
they'll get even further ahead of us.

272
00:19:26,870 --> 00:19:30,140
Tomorrow, we'll start to remove the snow from the field in the morning.

273
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:31,500
So get up early.

274
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:33,700
Speak more politely...

275
00:19:33,700 --> 00:19:36,670
I can't wake up by myself, so come pick me up.

276
00:19:36,670 --> 00:19:38,400
What have you done...?

277
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:41,770
Six o'clock ? 
Moron ! It's too early !

278
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,650
Honey...

279
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:48,800
Yeah, I guess that sounds right.

280
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:49,810
Okay.

281
00:19:51,700 --> 00:19:55,830
Huh ? What ? 
The snow is beautiful ?

282
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:58,870
You're still talking about that ?

283
00:19:58,870 --> 00:20:00,900
You have to live for the future ! 
For the future !

284
00:20:24,540 --> 00:20:31,450
Like that elm tree, I want to be someone who'll never change.

285
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:35,690
He remembered.

286
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:40,700
My treasure.

287
00:20:41,340 --> 00:20:43,920
It is my dream.

288
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:48,400
When I see that elm tree in the schoolyard, I always feel it.

289
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:55,550
In snow or rain, that elm tree has always encouraged me.

290
00:20:56,710 --> 00:21:00,730
That's why I want to
 be like that elm tree.

291
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:09,530
I like baseball. I like how everyone works hard and plays the game.

292
00:21:09,530 --> 00:21:15,660
I want other people to know this feeling, so I'd like to be a sports reporter.

293
00:21:15,660 --> 00:21:20,380
I think that, if I work hard like that elm tree, my dream will someday come true.

294
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:48,360
You think it's impossible, don't you ?

295
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:51,150
No, I think you can.

